info.name: Whatsapp Web Dark 127
info.description:
Dark mode for WhatsApp Web built from scratch using the internal variables from the original CSS.
Adds dark mode to all features. (If you find anything wrong with it please contact me)
info.additionalInfo:
Updated (19/06/2020):
Fixed colours for latest addition to whatsapp web on the chat bubbles, icons, secondary text and input.
Added missing search input background
Inverted default group icon
Set default border background on avatars to dark

Updated (05/06/2020):
Fixed latest additions to whatsapp web that broke the header colour and ack icons.
Fixed background image broken on latest whatsapp web update.
Fixed horizontal positioning and size for smaller screens.

First Version (06/05/2020):

Recently made and compatible with the most recent version of whatsapp web
Fixed intro background.
